data.description: Welcome to your charming and cozy 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom retreat in the heart of picturesque Ashland City! Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this lovingly maintained home is the perfect blend of comfort and affordability (with a Full Unfinished Basement/Bathroom for a possible expansion)! Outside, you'll find a generous yard with endless possibilities, perfect for gardening, outdoor play, or simply enjoying the fresh Tennessee air. The expansive backyard provides ample space for entertaining family and friends. This home's location is a standout feature, whether you're exploring the nearby scenic beauty of the Cumberland River or commuting to Nashville for work or entertainment, you'll find this location incredibly convenient. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming Ashland City house your new home!*See Features and Upgrades List for More Info
